1. *Posao* mi je dosadan. (My job is boring.)
2. Ona voli svoj *posao*. (She loves her job.)
3. Ona se preselila zbog *posla*. (She moved because of the job.)
4. Ona nije uspela da nađe *posao*. (She failed to find a job.)
5. Zašto ne tražiš *posao*? (Why don't you look for a job?)
6. *Posao* je završen. (The job is done.)
7. *Posao* me mnogo iscrpljuje. (The job exhausts me a lot.)
8. Ona je veoma uspešna u svom *poslu*. (She is very successful in her job.)